Hi Steve I've been watching your show since forever. Introduced via my kids and the fact that we have a very old black female cat who would be a match made in heaven for Sylvester. Don't worry about how long in between uploads you have just keep it up because selfishly it's one of the few things I get a kick out of on You Tube.
